flowchart TD
    A[block layout enters element] --> B[counter_push_scope]
    B --> C[setup_list_container_counters for OL UL MENU DIR]
    C --> D[counter_reset counter_increment counter_set from BlockProp]
    D --> E{is list item}
    E -- yes --> F[process_list_item]
    F --> G[handle li value, auto-increment list-item]
    G --> H[create_marker_element]
    H --> I[counter_format list-item into marker text]
    I --> J[MarkerProp on synthetic ::marker DomElement, view_type MARKER]
    E -- no --> K[layout children]
    J --> K
    K --> L[counter_pop_scope_propagate on leave]
